PRIVACY POLICY
Privacy Policy for Photo Compress & Resize
Effective Date
: 18-11-2024
Thank you for using
Photo Compress & Resize
. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your information when you use our application. By using our app, you agree to the terms outlined below.
1. Information We Collect
We value your privacy and ensure that your personal data is protected. The app may collect the following types of information:
•
Device Information
: We may collect anonymous data such as device type, operating system, and app usage statistics for performance and analytics purposes.
•
Images
: Images selected by the user are processed locally on your device for compression, resizing, or editing. No images or media files are uploaded to our servers.
2. How We Use Your Information
We do not collect any personal or sensitive data from users. The app processes images directly on your device. The information we collect is used for:
•
Enhancing app functionality and performance.
•
Resolving issues and improving the user experience.
•
Analytics to understand app usage trends (if applicable).
3. Data Security
We prioritize the security of your data and ensure:
•
No personal or image data is sent to external servers.
•
Images remain on your device during processing.
•
Industry-standard security measures protect any non-sensitive app data.
4. User Rights
You have full control over the data within the app:
•
All image processing is performed locally on your device.
•
You can uninstall the app at any time to delete all associated data.
5. Changes to This Privacy Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy periodically to reflect changes in our practices or legal requirements. Updates will be posted within the app, and the “Effective Date” will be revised.
7. Contact Us
If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at:
Email
: adilelbaayouiadil@gmail,.com
